Suzanne Cryer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Cryer 0 Suzanne Rossell Cryer (born January 13, 1967) is an American actress known for her roles as Ashley on the ABC sitcom Two Guys and a Girl and as Laurie Bream on the HBO original series, Silicon Valley. Cryer has also performed on Broadway.
